    "attributes": {
        "action": "Require schools to make every Friday a half day.",
        "additional_details": "Pupils are usually really tired by Friday, and if the day was a half day, the students wouldn't be as tired, which means they would look forward to it, and then they would work more productively in actual lesson time than just barely working and not doing much.",
        "background": "Change the timing so Friday will be a half day (in which pupils will go home at half the day)",
